channel.title: New Items?!?!?
channel.description:
Ok i am using hybridscape, and just trying to learn some Java coding before i actually make-make a server, so im just editing the java codes for hybridscape. So im using the built-in source for moparscape 3.0
Whenever i try to spawn items, like ::pickup 6570(firecape) 1 it will show a tz ket om(6539) in my INV same for anyother items in the 6100+ items. So any item like an onyx, fury, firecape,obby cape, ect, it will change to a tz ket om(obbymace -6539)
Got any idea on how to fix this?
Even when i try to make it show a fire cape in the stores, it shows tz ket om, and not the fire cape
If you can help, please post :)
Thanks.
